::DevilDuer::

DevilDuer nods, looking from Catgut to Threadshot. "I got a lock on 'er, she 
ain't gettin' away."

He glances at his scanner, "Allright, I'll take care of her. There's a battle 
going on not far from here, if you guys want some action, you can go join. 
Don' let the femm out though! Make sure to close blast doors behind ya."

He runs off down a hallway, slowing down as he approaches the cargo hold. 
Blast doors were closing behind him as he walked, and the same thing was 
happening at the cargo hold's end.

Gun out, DevilDuer walks forward, ready for battle.

"Hey, I don't wanna hurt ya," he yells to the hallway, "Just come out 
peacefully, you'll be allright."
